query:
SELECT 
  sourceType,
  COUNT(*) as total_without_url,
  MIN(lastUpdatedAt) as oldest_update,
  MAX(lastUpdatedAt) as newest_update
FROM properties 
WHERE sourceUrl IS NULL OR sourceUrl = ''
GROUP BY sourceType
ORDER BY total_without_url DESC;
